{
  "stem": "2097.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] And over there, I got a-- like a pistol, where I had to push the pin to come out.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And the automatically, the piece was turning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And the Germans, they gave us who worked there a mask, a robe-- a half a robe and a glove, and a 1/2 a liter skim milk every day, who worked on that place.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Painting.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, it's a round thing, it was turning.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think that was the satellite, or missiles, whatever they used, the Germans, with no man to bomb London and other places.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think they were the first who used and invented the missiles.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No-man missiles.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No it was-- it-- it was part of--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's part of that missiles.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In a certain place, was not allowed to let paint to go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And every day, three, four person was checking us all the time, that the paint shouldn't go there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The piece, what we painted, went on a chain to the dryer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And was something wrong, they brought it back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They put it back to wash.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then after, to paint again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because constantly, they were checking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had two-- three meisters over there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "One, a Czechoslovakian, one, a Ukrainian, and one, a German.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The-- as soon I worked over there and a few weeks after, my mouth started to bleed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I started to cough.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Probably the mask wasn't good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the paint, I don't know, if it get into my mouth or something.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the German meister, he brought for me a little piece, about a half a glass of salt to rinse my mouth.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "If they would caught him, I'm sure he would be severely punished.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He said, the [GERMAN], he said the [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I don't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
